                                    <div class="gdlr-core-pbf-wrapper " style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;">
                                        <div class="gdlr-core-pbf-element">
                                            <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-item gdlr-core-item-pdlr gdlr-core-item-pdb clearfix " style="padding-bottom: 25px ;">
                                                <ul>
                                                        
                                                        <li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 0px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #50bd77 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
                                                            <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 17px ;font-weight:700;">Guidelines for Visa</span></div>
                                                            <div class="gdlr-core-pbf-element">
                                            <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-item gdlr-core-item-pdlr gdlr-core-item-pdb clearfix " style="padding-bottom: 10px ;">
                                            <ul>
                                                <li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 15px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #192f59 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 18px ;"></span>Once Provisional Admission letter has been issued student should immediately apply for Student Visa at Indian Embassy / High Commission.</div>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 15px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #192f59 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 18px ;"></span>Ensure that your Student Visa is endorsed for CHARUSAT.</div>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 15px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #192f59 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 18px ;"></span>Change of University or Institution will not be considered by Government of India. In that case you would be required to go back to your home country and apply for a new visa.</div>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 15px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #192f59 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 18px ;"></span>Ensure, if you have entered India on basis of Student Visa endorsed for CHARUSAT, then you directly report to the CHARUSAT. As per Government of India rules, the Visa endorsed in the name of the University or obtained on the basis of University documents cannot be used for any other purpose like employment, admission to any other university/college/institute/academy etc. or for non-regular (distance/online) mode of education.</div>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 15px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #192f59 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 18px ;"></span>After reaching the University Campus, students have to get the visa verified by the University and have to deposit a copy of the valid visa at International Students’ Cell. It is the responsibility of the student to ensure that throughout his/her study period he/she is on valid visa.</div>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 15px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #192f59 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 18px ;"></span>ISC, CHARUSAT will help students in the above matters if contacted in time.</div>
                                                </li>
                                            </ul>
                                            </div>
                                                </div>
                                                        </li>
                                                        
                                                        <li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 0px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #50bd77 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
                                                            <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 17px ;font-weight:700;">Guidelines for Visa Extension and FRO/FRRO</span></div>
                                                            <div class="gdlr-core-pbf-element">
                                            <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-item gdlr-core-item-pdlr gdlr-core-item-pdb clearfix " style="padding-bottom: 10px ;">
                                            <ul>
                                                <li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 15px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #192f59 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 18px ;"></span>It is a mandatory for all International students except those from Nepal and Bhutan to get their Student Visa registered at FRRO/FRO within 14 days of arrival in India.</div>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 15px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #192f59 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 18px ;"></span>International Students’ Cell of CHARUSAT will guide and assist Student with all the required processes needed for FRO/FRRO Registration.</div>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 15px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #192f59 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 18px ;"></span>All International students except those from Nepal and Bhutan have to fill online application for Registration Certificate (RC) & Residential Permit (RP) on arrival to India at International Students’ Cell, CHARUSAT. ISC will help students in the above matters for filling the forms.</div>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 15px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #192f59 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 18px ;"></span>In case the initial visa is not endorsed for the complete duration of the program or student has to extend the stay because he/she is not able to complete the program in the stipulated time then the student should apply for the extension of the visa before visa expires.</div>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class=" gdlr-core-skin-divider" style="margin-bottom: 15px ;"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon-wrap" style="margin-top: 5px ;"><i class="gdlr-core-icon-list-icon fa fa-dot-circle-o" style="color: #192f59 ;font-size: 18px ;width: 18px ;" ></i></span>
                                                    <div class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content-wrap"><span class="gdlr-core-icon-list-content" style="font-size: 18px ;"></span>ISC, CHARUSAT will help students in the above matters if contacted in time.</div>
                                                </li>
                                            </ul>
                                            </div>
                                                </div>
                                                        </li>
                                                </ul>
                                        </div>
                                        </div>
                                   </div>
                                    
                                    
